author: Graeme McMillan
title: 5 Comics to Catch Up on While Self-Quarantined
description: Are you being a good citizen and staying at home? Good. Here are some comics to pass the time.
content: So, youre stuck at home and Netflix, Hulu, and even Disney+ are beginning to lose their luster after just a couple of weeks. (To be fair, thats probably because youve not watched The Rocketeer enough, but well let that slide for now.) With television and movi… [+3136 chars]
